tellar-love-and-gravity.html|work=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate=December 13, 2014|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205105243/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/21/opinion/david-brooks-interstellar-love-and-gravity.html|archivedate=December 5, 2014}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"la review of books\">{{cite web|url=http://lareviewofbooks.org/essay/books-space-christopher-nolans-interstellar|title=Books in Space: Christopher Nolan's \"Interstellar\"|first=Wai Chee|last=Dimock|date=December 25, 2014|work=The Los Angeles Review of Books|accessdate=March 20, 2015|archivedate=December 29, 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229234036/http://lareviewofbooks.org/essay/books-space-christopher-nolans-interstellar|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RRMartin\">{{cite journal|last=R. R. Martin|first=George|url=http://grrm.livejournal.com/410394.html|title=For Your Consideration: Stuff Not By Me|journal=Not a Blog|date=March 8, 2015|accessdate=May 23, 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150422021742/http://grrm.livejournal.com/410394.html|archivedate=April 22, 2015}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Oscar\">{{cite web|url=http://oscar.go.com/nominees |2= |title=The 87th Academy Award Nominations for the 2015 Oscars |date=January 15, 2015 |accessdate=January 15, 2015 |url-status=dead |website=oscar.go.com |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DZOQ92zN?url=http://oscar.go.com/nominees |archivedate=January 10, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"interstellar.withgoogle\">{{Cite web |url=https://interstellar.withgoogle.com/time-capsule |title=Emic  A Time Capsule from the People of Earth |website=interstellar.withgoogle.com |access-date=February 5, 2018 |url-status=bot: unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413223240/https://interstellar.withgoogle.com/time-capsule |archivedate=April 13, 2016  }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"googleforeducation\">{{Cite web |url=http://googleforeducation.blogspot.ca/2014/11/interstellar-lesson-plans-are-now.html |title=Google for Educagion Interstellar Lesson Plans are Now Available |website=googleforeducation.blogspot.ca |access-date=February 5, 2018 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205200847/http://googleforeducation.blogspot.ca/2014/11/interstellar-lesson-plans-are-now.html |archivedate=February 5, 2018 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"theguardian\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/gallery/2014/oct/29/interstellar-european-premiere-in-pictures |title=Interstellar European premiere \u2013 in pictures |work=[[The Guardian]] |access-date=February 5, 2018 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170310075449/https://www.theguardian.com/film/gallery/2014/oct/29/interstellar-european-premiere-in-pictures |archivedate=March 10, 2017  }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Lubin-Nov2014\">{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/how-hans-zimmer-wrote-the-interstellar-theme-2014-11?r=US&IR=T&IR=T|title=The Story Of How Hans Zimmer Wrote The 'Interstellar' Theme Will Give You Chills|first=Gus|last=Lubin|date=November 4, 2014|website=[[Business Insider]]|archivedate=July 19, 2018|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180719023335/http://www.businessinsider.com/how-hans-zimmer-wrote-the-interstellar-theme-2014-11?r=US&IR=T&IR=T|url-status=live|access-date=July 19, 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BluRay\">{{Citation|title=Interstellar 4K Blu-ray|url=http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Interstellar-4K-Blu-ray/187908/|accessdate=May 11, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511215907/http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Interstellar-4K-Blu-ray/187908/|archive-date=May 11, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Jessica Chastain Steals The Show At Interstellar European Premiere\">{{cite news | url= http://www.ikonlondonmagazine.com/jessica-chastain-steals-the-show-at-interstellar-world-premiere-in-london/ | title= Ikon London Magazine coverage from the London Premiere | work= Ikon London Magazine | date= October 30, 2014 | accessdate=